      <title>增长前景恶化，印度中型股进入调整期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/india-mid-cap-stocks-head-for-correction-as-growth-outlook-sours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者对盈利增长放缓和估值过高的担忧日益增加，中型股的强劲上涨即将进入回调区域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/india-mid-cap-stocks-head-for-correction-as-growth-outlook-sours</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 05:39:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Aquamarine 的 Spier 表示，《豪勇七蛟龙》近期不会上映</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/-magnificent-seven-won-t-fall-anytime-soon-aquamarine-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Aquamarine 创始人兼首席执行官 Guy Spier 表示：“七巨头不会很快分崩离析。”在接受彭博电视采访时，Spier 告诉 Haslinda Amin，包括苹果和特斯拉在内的科技股是“我们从未见过的”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/-magnificent-seven-won-t-fall-anytime-soon-aquamarine-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 05:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
